Empire is slotted for the eighth position in Saturday\u2019s Belmont Stakes. Just seven horses have won the Belmont Stakes from the eighth position. Angel of Empire is another entry from trainer Brad Cox and will be ridden by jockey Flavien Prat.<\/p>\r\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph --><a href=\"https:\/\/wp.winnersandwhiners.com\/horse-racing\/angel-of-empire-prediction-odds-and-profile-for-the-2023-belmont-stakes-620\/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https:\/\/wp.winnersandwhiners.com\/horse-racing\/angel-of-empire-prediction-odds-and-profile-for-the-2023-belmont-stakes-620\/\"><strong>Click here to read our complete profile &amp; prediction.<\/strong><\/a> <!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\r\n<!-- \/wp:column --><\/div>\r\n<!-- \/wp:columns -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:columns {\"isStackedOnMobile\":false} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile\"><!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"150px\"} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis: 150px;\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":583,\"sizeSlug\":\"thumbnail\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-thumbnail\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" class=\"wp-image-583\" src=\"https:\/\/wp.winnersandwhiners.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/USATSI_20740530-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" \/><\/figure>\r\n<!-- \/wp:image --><\/div>\r\n<!-- \/wp:column -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"75%\"} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis: 75%;\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\r\n<h3 id='red-route-one'  id=\"boomdevs_12\" class=\"wp-block-heading\" >Red Route One<\/h3>\r\n<!-- \/wp:heading -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"d-none d-sm-block\"} -->\r\n<p class=\"d-none d-sm-block\">Red Route One will be on the far outside at the Belmont Stakes, drawing the 9th position on Saturday. Only four horses in the history of the Belmont Stakes have won the race from the 9th spot. Red Route One was a late scratch from the